&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cloudflare is looking for a curious and driven Tax Intern to join our global Tax team. In this role, you’ll get a 360-degree view of a global corporate tax department. Whether you&#39;re assisting with quarterly provision calculations, researching US international tax concepts, or reconciling indirect tax data, you will be an active participant in our mission.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
